---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact — Alisia Martinez" description="Work inquiries, collaborations, and friendly hellos.">
  <section class="space-y-10">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <h1 class="h1">Contact ✦</h1>
        <img src="/doodles/sparkle.svg" alt="" class="mt-2 h-7 w-7" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg muted max-w-3xl">
        Want to build something people can feel? I’m open to work, collaborations, and friendly hellos.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <section class="card p-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="label">Work / consulting</div>
        <p class="muted">
          If you’re looking for a prototyper or experience designer—especially for ambiguous, high-leverage problems—tell me what you’re building.
        </p>
        <ul class="muted list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>rapid prototyping & interaction models</li>
          <li>systems behavior, edge cases, flows</li>
          <li>XR / immersive interaction design</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="card p-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="label">Collaborations / media</div>
        <p class="muted">
          I’m also building a broader creative brand—storytelling, events, and playful worldbuilding. If you have something weird and wonderful, I’m listening.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <section class="card p-8 space-y-4">
      <div class="label">Links</div>
      <p class="muted">
        Add your preferred contact methods here:
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
        <a class="card cardHover p-4 link-sparkle" href="mailto:you@example.com">Email</a>
        <a class="card cardHover p-4 link-sparkle" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/YOURHANDLE">LinkedIn</a>
        <a class="card cardHover p-4 link-sparkle" href="https://github.com/alisiamartz/portfolio26">GitHub</a>
        <a class="card cardHover p-4 link-sparkle" href="https://www.youtube.com/@YOURCHANNEL">YouTube</a>
      </div>

      <p class="muted text-xs">
        Tip: replace the placeholders with your real handles.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>